001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.BioPAXElement;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.ChemicalStructure;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.SmallMoleculeReference;
006
007
008public class SmallMoleculeReferenceImpl extends EntityReferenceImpl implements SmallMoleculeReference
009{
010        private String chemicalFormula;
011        private float molecularWeight = UNKNOWN_FLOAT;
012        private ChemicalStructure structure;
013
014        
015        public SmallMoleculeReferenceImpl() {
016        }
017
018        //
019        // utilityClass interface implementation
020        //
021        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
022
023    @Override
024        public Class<? extends SmallMoleculeReference> getModelInterface()
025        {
026                return SmallMoleculeReference.class;
027        }
028
029    public String getChemicalFormula()
030        {
031                return chemicalFormula;
032        }
033
034    public void setChemicalFormula(String formula)
035        {
036                chemicalFormula = formula;
037        }
038
039    // Property MOLECULAR-WEIGHT
040    
041    public float getMolecularWeight()
042        {
043                return molecularWeight;
044        }
045
046    public void setMolecularWeight(float molecularWeight)
047        {
048                this.molecularWeight = molecularWeight;
049        }
050
051    // Property structure
052    public ChemicalStructure getStructure()
053        {
054                return structure;
055        }
056
057    public void setStructure(ChemicalStructure structure)
058        {
059                this.structure = structure;
060        }
061    
062    @Override
063    protected boolean semanticallyEquivalent(BioPAXElement element) {
064        if(!(element instanceof SmallMoleculeReference)) return false;
065        SmallMoleculeReference that = (SmallMoleculeReference) element;
066        return (getChemicalFormula() != null 
067                        ? getChemicalFormula().equalsIgnoreCase(that.getChemicalFormula()) 
068                        : that.getChemicalFormula() == null)
069                && (getMolecularWeight() == that.getMolecularWeight())
070                && (getStructure() != null 
071                                ? getStructure().isEquivalent(that.getStructure()) 
072                        : that.getStructure() == null)
073                && super.semanticallyEquivalent(element);
074    }
075}
